#: .\effects.json
msgid "Resurrection Sickness"
msgstr ""

#. ~ Description of effect 'Resurrection Sickness'.
#: .\effects.json
msgid ""
"Your body is recovering from death. Your limbs are being forcibly stabilized"
" by mysterious energies."
msgstr ""

#. ~ Miss message for effect(s) 'Resurrection Sickness'.
#: .\effects.json
msgid "You feel your body forcibly reconstructing itself!"
msgstr ""

#. ~ Decay message for effect(s) 'Resurrection Sickness'.
#: .\effects.json
msgid "Your body has stabilized."
msgstr ""

#: .\effects.json
msgid "Warp Stability"
msgstr ""

#. ~ Description of effect 'Warp Stability'.
#: .\effects.json
msgid ""
"You're fresh from your stay at your sanctuary island.  The intangible miasma"
" of terra firma currently has no effect on you, and you feel fine.  This "
"should last for several hours.  Stay too long, however, and you'll gradually"
" begin to suffer ever-worsening debilitating effects."
msgstr ""

#: .\effects.json
msgid "Warp Sickness"
msgstr ""

#. ~ Description of effect 'Warp Sickness'.
#: .\effects.json
msgid ""
"You've overstayed your time earthside.  It's getting hard to concentrate, "
"there's a painful ringing in your ears, and your muscles sting and jolt.  "
"Every action feels delayed.  You need to warp home to refresh yourself, or "
"this is going to get worse.  Probably within just a few hours."
msgstr ""

#: .\effects.json
msgid "Warp Nausea"
msgstr ""

#. ~ Description of effect 'Warp Nausea'.
#: .\effects.json
msgid ""
"You've stayed earthside too long.  Your body aches and your senses are "
"dulling.  Every step feels like you're walking through thick mud and "
"breathing hot tar.  You should warp home as soon as you can, or this is only"
" going to get worse."
msgstr ""

#: .\effects.json
msgid "Warp Debilitation"
msgstr ""

#. ~ Description of effect 'Warp Debilitation'.
#: .\effects.json
msgid ""
"You've stayed earthside WAY too long!  Your body barely responds and your "
"senses are slush.  The world itself feels barbed and frayed, and the very "
"air is like breathing fiberglass.  If you want to survive, you need to warp "
"home as soon as possible."
msgstr ""

#: .\effects.json
msgid "Warp Necrosis"
msgstr ""

#. ~ Description of effect 'Warp Necrosis'.
#: .\effects.json
msgid ""
"The very fabric of your being is unraveling!  You're in dire straits.  You "
"need to get back to your sanctuary island NOW!"
msgstr ""

#: .\effects.json
msgid "Warp Disintegration!"
msgstr ""

#. ~ Description of effect 'Warp Disintegration!'.
#: .\effects.json
msgid ""
"You're going to die.  And if you weren't busy leaking blood out of every "
"pore, you'd find a better way to emphasize just how badly you're dying.  "
"Your only hope is to return home immediately."
msgstr ""

#: .\effects.json
msgid "Disintegrating!"
msgstr ""

#. ~ Description of effect 'Disintegrating!'.
#: .\effects.json
msgid "Prolonged warp is destroying you.  You're coming apart."
msgstr ""

#. ~ Apply message for effect(s) 'Disintegrating!'.
#: .\effects.json
msgid "You're being unmade!"
msgstr ""

#. ~ Remove message for effect(s) 'Disintegrating!'.
#: .\effects.json
msgid ""
"The rending of the warp has finally abated.  You feel like you exist again."
msgstr ""

#: .\effects.json
msgid "Warp Cloak"
msgstr ""

#. ~ Description of effect 'Warp Cloak'.
#: .\effects.json
msgid ""
"You are invisible and incorporeal for a brief time. Now's your chance to get"
" to cover. You also won't take fall damage."
msgstr ""

#. ~ Apply message for effect(s) 'Warp Cloak'.
#: .\effects.json
msgid "Warp energy envelops you!"
msgstr ""

#. ~ Remove message for effect(s) 'Warp Cloak'.
#: .\effects.json
msgid "You fully materialize. You're not invisible anymore!"
msgstr ""

#. ~ Decay message for effect(s) 'Warp Cloak'.
#: .\effects.json
msgid "Your warpcloak is about to fade away."
msgstr ""

#: .\effects.json
msgid "Warped Omniscience"
msgstr ""

#. ~ Description of effect 'Warped Omniscience'.
#: .\effects.json
msgid "Nothing escapes your sight."
msgstr ""

#. ~ Apply message for effect(s) 'Warped Omniscience'.
#: .\effects.json
msgid "Your vision expands until you see everything."
msgstr ""

#. ~ Remove message for effect(s) 'Warped Omniscience'.
#: .\effects.json
msgid "Your sight returns to normal."
msgstr ""

